·        "Calidore" (c. 1816)

·        "The Pilgrim of Provence" (c. 1826)

·        "The Lord of the Hills" (c. 1835)

·        "Julia Procula" (c. 1850)

·        "A Story Opening at Chertsey" (c. 1850)

